# Python (src layout)

## Package

`src/ai_control_plane/` — import as `ai_control_plane.*`.

## Module boundaries

- `cli/` → HTTP/API only; no direct `core/policies` imports in CLI paths.
- `mcp/git_server.py` — sole Git facade.
- `api/` — TypeScript bridge; schema changes need `docs/CONTRACT_TESTS.md` check.

## Style

- Pydantic v2, structlog, async I/O where existing code does.
- Surgical diff only — no drive-by refactors.

## Verify (minimum)

```bash
ruff check src/ tests/
mypy src/ai_control_plane/ --strict
pytest tests/ -v
```
